net.sf.tweety.logics.rpcl

Class ReferenceWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.tweety.commons.AbstractInterpretation
      • net.sf.tweety.logics.rpcl.ReferenceWorld
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<net.sf.tweety.logics.commons.syntax.Predicate,InstanceAssignment>, net.sf.tweety.commons.Interpretation

    public class ReferenceWorld
extends net.sf.tweety.commons.AbstractInterpretation
implements Map<net.sf.tweety.logics.commons.syntax.Predicate,InstanceAssignment>
    Instances of this class represent reference worlds, i.e. sets of instance assignment. Each reference world describes a set of Herbrand interpretations.
    Author:
    Matthias Thimm
